# ---------------------------------------------------------
*.o
*.obj
*.lo
*.la
*.a
*.lib
*.so
*.so.*
*.dll
*.dylib
*.exe
*.app

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Logs
# ---------------------------------------------------------
*.log

# ---------------------------------------------------------
